title: Booking Contest from Delta Vacations and Aeromexico Vacations
text:
Marilee Crocker Booking Contest from Delta Vacations and Aeromexico Vacations 
Travel agents can win a free trip for two to the Grand Fiesta Americans Los Cabos All Inclusive Golf & Spa through a contest being sponsored by Delta Vacations and Aeromexico Vacations. The agents with the most qualified bookings of six nights or longer to Los Cabos by Sept. 30 will receive the trip. Agents booking trips to Los Cabos can save up to $200 per booking through Delta with the promotional code DV20204. Go to the website for complete details. 0
